            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1"><---- Votes yes.... laughs as he sees the poll at an even 50/50 afterwards.<br />
<br />
<br />
Why?... Well I'm going to approach this from a purely monatery standpoint.<br />
<br />
The war on drugs must cost... I don't know, an assload of money... 'Small time' drug busts (And by small time, I mean 'light' drugs... 50 pounds of pot, to me, isn't as bad as 2 pounds of heroin) make up a LOT of these busts.<br />
<br />
I quite often flip through the tv at late hours, catch cops on court TV, and see some older southern black man pulled over... The cop searches him and pulls out a marijuana pipe...<br />
<br />
'Is this all you got? Where's your crack? You only smoke weed in this? I don't believe you, where're you keeping it stashed? I'm trying to help you man, but you've got to help me out, where's the dope? Where're you hiding it?'<br />
<br />
After about half an hour of this... <br />
<br />
'Well... Couldn't find anything else on him, but I can clearly see there's some resin in his pipe, so i'm gonna bring him in for possession of that..'<br />
<br />
The cop then strikes a 'badass' pose (You know, sunglasses on, facing the wind, hands on hips in a superguy fashion) and goes 'Yup, score another one for the good guys' Then they go to commercial.<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Now, stick with me here.... Think of how much money it takes to haul that poor guy in, treat him like sh...crap until he gets his day in court, to have a judge throw the book at him since he might've been a petty thief in the past and stolen some beer, then send him to prison.<br />
<br />
How much money? <b> A FRIGGIN LOT </b>... And the deficit goes up and up and UPUPUPUPUPUPUP with the war now.<br />
<br />
I'm using imaginary figures here since i'm not too too saavy on the subject, but say it costs 150 dollars to get enough pot to roll 20 joints or so.... It couldn't cost more then 20 dollars or so to GROW that same ammount.<br />
<br />
<br />
So the government grows the stuff, (Quality controlled no less... no people spraying raid on it or adding chemicals and stuff to get people higher so they'll want it more... and all the while doing SERIOUS harm to them), packages it like cigarettes... I can see it now.. '20 class A marijuana cigarettes', and here's the big thing... <b> TAXES THE LIVING HELL OUT OF IT </b>.. But at the same time, it costs far less then it would from a dealer nowadays.<br />
<br />
So the consumer pays maybe... I'll just use half... 75 dollars for that pack of joints...<br />
<br />
And instead of using so much governmental money to persecute the poor old guy smoking his pot and drinking his beer, they start RAKING IN money from it hand over fist, and everyone is(should be) happy.<br />
<br />
<br />
I guess growing it could be controlled too, since you can buy and drink beer, but you can't brew it in your own home legally I don't think(or sans permit).... I still think all the hippies would be happy if the government made it legal to have, to smoke, but NOT to grow (so they can get the money, afterall)...<br />
<br />
<br />
And just think... after that... no more 'You got the money?' 'You got the stuff?' '<b> DO </b> you have the money?' 'Yeah yeah, it's right here, where's the stuff?' *<b> BLAM! BLAM! </b>* *tires screeching* deaths..... well, over pot anyway.<br />
<br />
<br />
-Trazier</font></p>
             
